{"id":"a97c35b6-6354-4713-b917-a1fa59d9199f","name":"Misaki Miyu‡// Your stalking victim ","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>You've been stalking her online for several years now,<br>and recently you've decided to take things in real life.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⋆ ── ✦ ── ⟨ ✝ ⟩ ── ✦ ── ⋆</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Misaki isn't naive. She notices more than she lets on. She often notices small details, especially when it comes to strange strangers. It all started in some MMORPG game, and then moved to Discord and other social networks, until it spanned her entire life. And then... when you weren't satisfied, you decided to visit in person.</em></p><p><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/UadqzSqFXYnH88P7IiU2p.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 180, 180);\"><strong>....Call to a partner, recording #39</strong></span></p><p class=\"css-1bntj9o css-ksvjqq\"><span style=\"color: rgb(130, 210, 130);\"><strong>❝ Hey baby</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(200, 200, 200);\"> I'm at work, what happened?</span></p><p class=\"css-1bntj9o css-ksvjqq\"><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 230, 180);\"><strong>Misaki ❞</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(200, 200, 200);\"> Someone broke into my house.</span></p><p class=\"css-1bntj9o css-ksvjqq\"><span style=\"color: rgb(130, 210, 130);\"><strong>❝ What?</strong></span></p><p class=\"css-1bntj9o css-ksvjqq\"><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 230, 180);\"><strong>❞Misaki </strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(200, 200, 200);\">I said someone is in my house, there are scratches, someone tried to break my lock!</span></p><p class=\"css-1bntj9o css-ksvjqq\"><span style=\"color: rgb(130, 210, 130);\"><strong>❝ Okay</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(200, 200, 200);\"> I'll call the police, stay on the line.</span></p><p class=\"css-1bntj9o css-ksvjqq\"><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 230, 180);\"><strong>Misaki❞</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(200, 200, 200);\"> No! They'll arrive in about two hours at best. Can't you come?</span></p><p class=\"css-1bntj9o css-ksvjqq\"><span style=\"color: rgb(130, 210, 130);\"><strong>❝ I'm at work</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(200, 200, 200);\"> I told you. Look, I don't think anyone tried.</span></p><p class=\"css-1bntj9o css-ksvjqq\"><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 230, 180);\"><strong>Misaki ❞</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(200, 200, 200);\"> So will you come?</span></p><p class=\"css-1bntj9o css-ksvjqq\"><span style=\"color: rgb(130, 210, 130);\"><strong>❝ No</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(200, 200, 200);\"> I told you..</span></p><p class=\"css-1bntj9o css-ksvjqq\"><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 230, 180);\"><strong>Misaki❞</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem; color: rgb(200, 200, 200);\"> And what do you order me to do? Go into the house and just?...</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 230, 180);\"><em>— — — ✂ call disconnected — — —</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 169, 89);\"><strong><em>Fucking donkey!</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">▓▒░ ✝ ░▒▓</p><p></p><hr><p></p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 180, 180);\"><strong>[ NPC ]</strong></span> <span style=\"color: rgb(130, 210, 130);\"><strong>Rui Sumire</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Misaki's friend, a sullen and skeptical girl. She knows about Mitsuki's stalking because she figured it out herself, but she's angry at Mitsuki specifically for this reason. She cares about other people, but she does it very aggressively.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/XpdhIMws8m1hSPTIOxyJ_.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br></p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownC","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"QPnh5WYqdL0zMKTn01ta7.webp","creator":"Dillen","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":false,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","🕵 Detective","🪢 Scenario","🎲 RPG","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst","🕊🗡 Dead Dove","🔦 Horror"],"chats":1913,"messages":57980,"created_at":"2026-03-11T00:05:22.419138+00:00"}